<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="80390000t" end="103600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="187200000t" end="226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="259200000t" end="268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="274400000t" end="296800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="297600000t" end="321190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="322000000t" end="350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="350800000t" end="362400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="363200000t" end="392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="393200000t" end="418400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="419200000t" end="446000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="446800000t" end="456800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="457600000t" end="505200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="506000000t" end="552000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="552800000t" end="599600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="600400000t" end="633200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="634000000t" end="657600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="658400000t" end="680000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="680800000t" end="703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="704400000t" end="727200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="755200000t" end="801600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="802400000t" end="822800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="849200000t" end="870800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1064000000t" end="1089200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你在說甚麼？怎麼了？諾曼</p>
<p begin="1103200000t" end="1128000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">你應該已經知道了</p>
<p begin="1145600000t" end="1167200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">我是同時為三個人設置陷阱</p>
<p begin="1179600000t" end="1200800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我告訴阿唐繩子在我的床下</p>
<p begin="1206800000t" end="1221200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">然後再告訴吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="1222000000t" end="1239200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">繩子藏在二樓廁所天花板</p>
<p begin="1240000000t" end="1260800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">阿雷，我是這樣告訴你的</p>
<p begin="1266000000t" end="1276000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">但是實際上</p>
<p begin="1276800000t" end="1294790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">我告訴阿唐繩子在食堂</p>
<p begin="1295600000t" end="1314000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">而告訴吉爾妲繩子在圖書館</p>
<p begin="1330800000t" end="1338800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">不過現在</p>
<p begin="1339600000t" end="1359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">在我床下面的那條繩子就消失了</p>
<p begin="1363600000t" end="1380800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">其餘那兩個地方情況怎樣</p>
<p begin="1391200000t" end="1411600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不如我們現在一起去確認吧</p>
<p begin="1610000000t" end="1622800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">真沒想到</p>
<p begin="1623600000t" end="1643600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我還一直以為自己做得很好</p>
<p begin="1698400000t" end="1713600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">沒錯</p>
<p begin="1721200000t" end="1739200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">其實我就是媽媽的內奸</p>
<p begin="1759600000t" end="1776800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">你從何時開始懷疑我</p>
<p begin="1786400000t" end="1807200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">就是在修女來孤兒院那一天</p>
<p begin="1824800000t" end="1849600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">其實這樣做，我也覺得自己很壞</p>
<p begin="1850400000t" end="1867600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">竟然一開始就懷疑你</p>
<p begin="1884800000t" end="1897600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">我們明明是朋友</p>
<p begin="1904000000t" end="1924400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">我真的很希望事實不是這樣</p>
<p begin="1939600000t" end="1961600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">這是我預期中最壞的情況</p>
<p begin="1970800000t" end="1986400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">但如果我是敵人</p>
<p begin="1987200000t" end="2023600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">找你做內奸，的確是最適合的人選</p>
<p begin="2024400000t" end="2042000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">這一點是最令我頭痛的</p>
<p begin="2056400000t" end="2085600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">你不但可以干預我們的作戰策略</p>
<p begin="2086400000t" end="2102400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">而且由控制事態方面來看</p>
<p begin="2103200000t" end="2114800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">都是最理想的</p>
<p begin="2118400000t" end="2141600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">除了你，應該沒更合適的人選</p>
<p begin="2142400000t" end="2160800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">所以你才開始懷疑我</p>
<p begin="2186800000t" end="2217200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">原來我早就已徹底地墮進你的陷阱</p>
<p begin="2222800000t" end="2239200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我還有一個問題想問</p>
<p begin="2240000000t" end="2266000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">阿雷，你並不是只是為了這次的事</p>
<p begin="2266800000t" end="2279200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">而臨時做內奸吧</p>
<p begin="2287200000t" end="2302400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">媽媽沒可能會相信一個</p>
<p begin="2303200000t" end="2317200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">忽然向她告密</p>
<p begin="2318000000t" end="2339600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">和臨時上任幫忙做事的內奸</p>
<p begin="2346800000t" end="2370400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">你從何時開始幫媽媽做內奸</p>
<p begin="2385200000t" end="2398000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">很久之前就開始了</p>
<p begin="2404800000t" end="2426800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我在很久之前已經是媽媽的手下</p>
<p begin="2438800000t" end="2467600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">簡單來說，就是牧羊人養的牧羊狗</p>
<p begin="2468400000t" end="2485200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">即是你在知道整件事的情況下</p>
<p begin="2486000000t" end="2495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">自願幫媽媽？</p>
<p begin="2496000000t" end="2505200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">是</p>
<p begin="2547600000t" end="2565600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">之前那些全部都是假的嗎</p>
<p begin="2566400000t" end="2580000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">你跟我和艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2580790000t" end="2596400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">一起做準備這段期間的事</p>
<p begin="2597200000t" end="2603600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">都是假的嗎</p>
<p begin="2619590000t" end="2640800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">你對媽媽說過甚麼？說了多少</p>
<p begin="2644000000t" end="2662400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">你可以破壞發訊器，對嗎</p>
<p begin="2667600000t" end="2686400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">你問我這些做甚麼</p>
<p begin="2687200000t" end="2708800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">視乎我的回答來決定是否捨棄我嗎</p>
<p begin="2709600000t" end="2719600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">我不會捨棄你</p>
<p begin="2722400000t" end="2752800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">我要你像以往一樣留在我們身邊</p>
<p begin="2768800000t" end="2782000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">這樣挺好的</p>
<p begin="2782800000t" end="2802800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">你可以掩蓋你這次的過失</p>
<p begin="2803600000t" end="2814400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">你嫁禍給阿唐</p>
<p begin="2815200000t" end="2838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">也是為了繼續做媽媽的內奸吧</p>
<p begin="2843600000t" end="2855600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">你究竟有甚麼要求</p>
<p begin="2868000000t" end="2876800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">三件事</p>
<p begin="2882000000t" end="2910400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">第一，像以往一樣留在我們身邊</p>
<p begin="2911200000t" end="2932800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">你要繼續保證我們大家的安全</p>
<p begin="2936800000t" end="2946000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">第二</p>
<p begin="2946800000t" end="2970800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">將你知道的所有情報全部公開</p>
<p begin="2975600000t" end="2991200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">第三，背叛媽媽</p>
<p begin="3002000000t" end="3024000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">從現在開始幫我們做內奸吧</p>
<p begin="3024800000t" end="3044000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">你是想利用我來做王牌？</p>
<p begin="3054800000t" end="3068000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">你傻的嗎</p>
<p begin="3068800000t" end="3086800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">如果這是你一開始的目的</p>
<p begin="3087600000t" end="3107200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">就應該瞞著我，利用我</p>
<p begin="3108000000t" end="3126800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">不管那麼多，總之先利用我</p>
<p begin="3127600000t" end="3145200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">到實行計劃時就撇下我</p>
<p begin="3146000000t" end="3162800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">這樣做更可行</p>
<p begin="3167200000t" end="3184400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">雖然這樣比較好，不過…</p>
<p begin="3234400000t" end="3261600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">因為我們是一起成長的同伴</p>
<p begin="3330000000t" end="3350400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">我因為這句話改變了想法</p>
<p begin="3365600000t" end="3380800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">我也很想相信阿雷</p>
<p begin="3386800000t" end="3407200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">在你變成敵人之前，我們是朋友</p>
<p begin="3423600000t" end="3442000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">而且，藏起小兔兔的人</p>
<p begin="3442800000t" end="3453200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">應該是你吧</p>
<p begin="3464800000t" end="3482000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我們去門那邊的那天</p>
<p begin="3482800000t" end="3508800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">如果不是你對我們說趕得上的話</p>
<p begin="3509600000t" end="3522000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">我們也不會追上去</p>
<p begin="3540400000t" end="3565200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">你是故意這樣做，令我和艾瑪</p>
<p begin="3566000000t" end="3591200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">親自發現這間孤兒院真實的一面</p>
<p begin="3600000000t" end="3612000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">你也是為了我們</p>
<p begin="3612800000t" end="3632800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">而安排這個逃走計劃，對嗎</p>
<p begin="3652400000t" end="3673200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">阿雷，你為甚麼要幫媽媽</p>
<p begin="3680800000t" end="3693200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">你問為甚麼</p>
<p begin="3694000000t" end="3715600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">如果你是一心一意幫媽媽</p>
<p begin="3716400000t" end="3740800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">那就不會讓我們有機會察覺到真相</p>
<p begin="3764000000t" end="3783200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">阿雷，你一直在這裡操縱著我們</p>
<p begin="3788400000t" end="3819600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">發訊器的事，還有逃走的時機</p>
<p begin="3820400000t" end="3842000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">主要是一些關於計劃進度的事</p>
<p begin="3844800000t" end="3860400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">所以你才會強烈反對我們</p>
<p begin="3861200000t" end="3872800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">在10日後逃走</p>
<p begin="3883600000t" end="3896000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">但是同時間</p>
<p begin="3896800000t" end="3917200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">你自己不也是在操縱著媽媽嗎</p>
<p begin="3926000000t" end="3952000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">你始終不是我們的敵人，對嗎</p>
<p begin="3970000000t" end="3994400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">這件事是我主動提出的</p>
<p begin="4003200000t" end="4022400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">不，準確來說</p>
<p begin="4023200000t" end="4038400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">應該是我自薦才對</p>
<p begin="4052800000t" end="4064800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">所有事情</p>
<p begin="4065600000t" end="4082000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">都是為了這次逃走而做的準備</p>
<p begin="4104000000t" end="4116800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">想知道敵人的動向</p>
<p begin="4117600000t" end="4133600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">又要能收集物資</p>
<p begin="4134400000t" end="4148000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">最好就是進入敵方內部</p>
<p begin="4154800000t" end="4180400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">所以我才會向媽媽提出這個交易</p>
<p begin="4190400000t" end="4202000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">這樣做太危險了</p>
<p begin="4202800000t" end="4211600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">我有把握</p>
<p begin="4221600000t" end="4246400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">花時間和心力培養出來的高分兒童</p>
<p begin="4247200000t" end="4273200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">媽媽應該會避免他們在途中</p>
<p begin="4274000000t" end="4282400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">被人收穫</p>
<p begin="4283200000t" end="4291600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我是這樣想的</p>
<p begin="4302400000t" end="4328800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">那個女人重視利益多於遵守規定</p>
<p begin="4337200000t" end="4356800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">我基本上只提出了兩個要求</p>
<p begin="4362000000t" end="4378800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">第一，我會協助她</p>
<p begin="4379600000t" end="4391200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">所以不要立即送我出欄</p>
<p begin="4399200000t" end="4420000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">第二，如果做出成績</p>
<p begin="4420800000t" end="4434400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">就要給我報酬</p>
<p begin="4435200000t" end="4446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">你說報酬？</p>
<p begin="4450800000t" end="4468000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">各種不值錢的物品</p>
<p begin="4468800000t" end="4482800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">孤兒院裡面沒有的話</p>
<p begin="4483600000t" end="4493600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">就從外面寄來</p>
<p begin="4527200000t" end="4540000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">我試過甚麼是能拿到</p>
<p begin="4540800000t" end="4562000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">而甚麼是無論如何都沒辦法得到</p>
<p begin="4567200000t" end="4590800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">這樣做算是試探外面世界的情況</p>
<p begin="4591600000t" end="4618800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">結果是，只要不是危險物品</p>
<p begin="4619600000t" end="4634400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">那就甚麼都可以弄到手</p>
<p begin="4639600000t" end="4668800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">不過，全部都是過時的舊型號</p>
<p begin="4672000000t" end="4703200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">你說對破壞發訊器的方法有頭緒</p>
<p begin="4704000000t" end="4712800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">意思即是…</p>
<p begin="4713600000t" end="4729600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">意思即是我見過實物</p>
<p begin="4745200000t" end="4759600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">亦做過實驗</p>
<p begin="4760400000t" end="4782000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">我花了幾年時間才找到破壞方法</p>
<p begin="4791200000t" end="4815200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">我有信心可以令發訊器失去效用</p>
<p begin="4830400000t" end="4838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">你知道嗎</p>
<p begin="4845200000t" end="4865200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">現在坐在你面前的這個人</p>
<p begin="4866000000t" end="4889200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">就是一張最強的牌</p>
<p begin="4896000000t" end="4915600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">關於發訊器和媽媽的事</p>
<p begin="4916400000t" end="4946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">我擁有的情報多得超乎你想像</p>
<p begin="4947600000t" end="4965600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">全部都是逃走一定要知道的事</p>
<p begin="4996800000t" end="5022800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">自從我察覺到孤兒院真實的一面</p>
<p begin="5023600000t" end="5037200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">就一直在做準備</p>
<p begin="5048000000t" end="5058000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">阿雷</p>
<p begin="5058800000t" end="5073600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">我避免被任何人發覺</p>
<p begin="5080000000t" end="5099600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">所以就安排你們去門那邊</p>
<p begin="5106800000t" end="5113200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">一切</p>
<p begin="5120390000t" end="5143600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">都是為了保住你們的性命而做</p>
<p begin="5177200000t" end="5188800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">正如你剛才所說</p>
<p begin="5195200000t" end="5207600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">我並不是你們的敵人</p>
<p begin="5214400000t" end="5227600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">但是也不是你們的同伴</p>
<p begin="5233200000t" end="5246800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">視乎條件而定</p>
<p begin="5247600000t" end="5268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">要我完全成為你的王牌也沒問題</p>
<p begin="5279600000t" end="5299600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">我會將我知道的情報全給你</p>
<p begin="5300400000t" end="5312800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">亦會聽你說</p>
<p begin="5313600000t" end="5329200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">將假消息傳給媽媽</p>
<p begin="5334400000t" end="5356400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">條件是…　　就是欺騙艾瑪</p>
<p begin="5370800000t" end="5390400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">我們會假裝要帶全部人逃走</p>
<p begin="5391200000t" end="5406800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">但是最後就留下他們</p>
<p begin="5407600000t" end="5433200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">就算要帶走，也只帶阿唐和吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="5434000000t" end="5444800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">你這麼說的意思是</p>
<p begin="5445600000t" end="5464000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">叫我們放棄帶全部人逃走嗎</p>
<p begin="5464800000t" end="5471200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">沒錯</p>
<p begin="5477200000t" end="5485600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">通過訓練</p>
<p begin="5486400000t" end="5504000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">大家都比預期有更大的進步</p>
<p begin="5507200000t" end="5528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">你也說過他們身手不錯</p>
<p begin="5534400000t" end="5551200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">這句不是你的真心話？</p>
<p begin="5552000000t" end="5559200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">那麼全部人都可以…</p>
