<p begin="6740800000t" end="6756800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">你怎麼這麼遲才來</p>
<p begin="6757600000t" end="6787200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我剛才跟諾曼談過　　然後呢</p>
<p begin="6792800000t" end="6804800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">目前沒甚麼變化</p>
<p begin="6810800000t" end="6829200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">還是全情投入捉迷藏訓練</p>
<p begin="6836000000t" end="6858400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">問題是那個修女</p>
<p begin="6859200000t" end="6875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">她又再擅自行動</p>
<p begin="6879200000t" end="6904800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">多注意她比較好　　是嗎</p>
<p begin="6912800000t" end="6938800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">你根本就不應該叫那個修女來</p>
<p begin="6939600000t" end="6970400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">難道你叫她來是為了要壓制我</p>
