<p begin="7173200000t" end="7190400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">都做不好，我真的很失望</p>
<p begin="7191200000t" end="7212800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">所以我就做內奸，挽回過失</p>
