<p begin="8534200000t" end="8555800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">所以我迫不得已要控制情況</p>
<p begin="8556600000t" end="8569800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">而且你們又亂來</p>
<p begin="8570600000t" end="8583000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">好像快要失控一樣</p>
<p begin="8583800000t" end="8601000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">於是我就先不說</p>
