<p begin="8668600000t" end="8680200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">但是還是覺得</p>
<p begin="8681000000t" end="8704600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">我們不應該帶全部人一起逃走嗎</p>
<p begin="8705400000t" end="8719400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">不過現在不同了</p>
<p begin="8726600000t" end="8747800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">我會協助你們帶全部人逃走</p>
