<p begin="8851400000t" end="8873400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">我很開心，阿雷再一次說</p>
<p begin="8874200000t" end="8894600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">他會幫忙帶全部人一起逃走</p>
<p begin="8899800000t" end="8915000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">而且這次還讓我們知道了</p>
<p begin="8915800000t" end="8940200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">我們可以由內部欺騙媽媽</p>
