<p begin="8974600000t" end="8993000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">不過…原來是這樣</p>
<p begin="9003800000t" end="9030600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">你一直都知道整件事的真相</p>
