<p begin="9335800000t" end="9354200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">而成為新的犧牲品，對嗎</p>
<p begin="9374600000t" end="9395400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">算了，沒事，謝謝你</p>
<p begin="9396200000t" end="9420200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">多虧你，現在可以大家一起逃走了</p>
<p begin="9431400000t" end="9475400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">但是你以後不要再劃界線</p>
<p begin="9476200000t" end="9487400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">來孤立自己</p>
<p begin="9502600000t" end="9519000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">你已經不再孤伶伶</p>
<p begin="9527800000t" end="9539800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">不是孤獨一人</p>
<p begin="9569400000t" end="9595800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">我向你發誓，以後不會再這樣做</p>
<p begin="9603400000t" end="9621000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">大家一起逃出這裡吧</p>
<p begin="9649800000t" end="9685800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">艾瑪他們還是三個人一起在討論</p>
<p begin="9691400000t" end="9726600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">可惡，他們三人究竟要商量到何時</p>
<p begin="9727400000t" end="9751800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">如果我們再不快些出去救柯妮</p>
<p begin="9752600000t" end="9771000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">不知道是否有其他的原因</p>
<p begin="9771800000t" end="9783000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">甚麼原因</p>
<p begin="9787800000t" end="9802600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">我也不清楚</p>
<p begin="9803400000t" end="9827000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">有可能不但是因為對方是一群壞人</p>
<p begin="9827800000t" end="9841800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">所以情況很危險</p>
<p begin="9847400000t" end="9872200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">而是其他更沉重的事情</p>
<p begin="9926600000t" end="9942600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">艾瑪覺得生氣</p>
<p begin="9951400000t" end="9978600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">對了，阿雷，我有件事想問你</p>
<p begin="9983800000t" end="9989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">甚麼事</p>
<p begin="9995400000t" end="10007400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">你之前說過</p>
<p begin="10008200000t" end="10015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">一切都是為了</p>
<p begin="10016200000t" end="10031800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">保住我們二人的性命而做</p>
<p begin="10037400000t" end="10049800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">難道你…</p>
<p begin="10050600000t" end="10059800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">對了</p>
<p begin="10077000000t" end="10096600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">有一件事要向你們報告</p>
<p begin="10128200000t" end="10141400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">最近我跟吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="10142200000t" end="10170600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">一起重新仔細觀察過媽媽一段時間</p>
<p begin="10176200000t" end="10200600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">媽媽在每晚8時之前都會不知去向</p>
<p begin="10203400000t" end="10215800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">不知去向？</p>
<p begin="10216600000t" end="10222200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">對</p>
<p begin="10227000000t" end="10247000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">在孤兒院裡看不到她的蹤影</p>
<p begin="10256600000t" end="10277800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">那麼即是孤兒院裡有秘密房間</p>
<p begin="10278590000t" end="10290200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">秘密房間？</p>
<p begin="10290990000t" end="10313390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">沒錯，位置是這裡</p>
<p begin="10327000000t" end="10350200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">就是在媽媽的睡房旁邊</p>
<p begin="10350990000t" end="10365790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">媽媽的睡房位置</p>
<p begin="10366600000t" end="10389800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">旁邊有洗手間和化妝間</p>
<p begin="10392200000t" end="10404200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">而中間這道牆的作用</p>
<p begin="10405000000t" end="10429000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">應該就是用來隔開媽媽的書房</p>
<p begin="10442200000t" end="10462200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">不過這裡可能不是牆</p>
<p begin="10473800000t" end="10498200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">我也發現到了，媽媽每一次</p>
<p begin="10499000000t" end="10519000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">在失蹤之前都一定會進去書房</p>
<p begin="10519800000t" end="10533400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">或者化妝間裡</p>
<p begin="10534200000t" end="10575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">然後我們在房間裡面和走廊上</p>
<p begin="10576200000t" end="10592600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">分別測量過它們的距離</p>
<p begin="10603400000t" end="10613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">所以那時…</p>
<p begin="10627000000t" end="10652200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">那麼結果呢　　距離不一致</p>
<p begin="10661800000t" end="10687800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">相差大約有我10個腳掌長的差距</p>
<p begin="10694600000t" end="10722600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">一邊是牆壁，而另一邊就是書架</p>
<p begin="10730200000t" end="10757400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">我覺得兩邊都分別有一道暗門</p>
<p begin="10758200000t" end="10787400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">而暗門的另一邊就是那個秘密房間</p>
<p begin="10788200000t" end="10804200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">但是這個房間有甚麼用途</p>
<p begin="10805000000t" end="10824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">有可能是用來…　　定期聯絡</p>
<p begin="10830600000t" end="10840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">因為媽媽每天</p>
<p begin="10841400000t" end="10859400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">都會跟總部那邊定期聯絡</p>
<p begin="10860200000t" end="10874200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">應該就是這個用途</p>
<p begin="10883400000t" end="10893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">總部？</p>
<p begin="10893800000t" end="10912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">意思即是為這間孤兒院</p>
<p begin="10913400000t" end="10931800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">提供嬰兒和修女的據點</p>
<p begin="10942600000t" end="10955800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">阿雷，你早就知道了嗎</p>
<p begin="10956600000t" end="10971400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">知道這個位置有一個房間？</p>
<p begin="10972200000t" end="10980600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">我不知道</p>
<p begin="10981400000t" end="10996200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">但曾懷疑有這樣的房間</p>
<p begin="10997000000t" end="11008200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">我們進去看看吧</p>
<p begin="11009000000t" end="11029800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">找聯繫外面的通訊方法</p>
<p begin="11030600000t" end="11049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">還有柯妮，他們的位置在哪裡</p>
<p begin="11049800000t" end="11071800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我們說不定可以找到其他線索</p>
<p begin="11072600000t" end="11097400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">不過我們會這麼容易就能進去嗎</p>
<p begin="11098200000t" end="11118600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">就算多困難，我們也要試試</p>
<p begin="11119400000t" end="11145400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">等等，其實根本不值得我們這樣做</p>
<p begin="11149400000t" end="11164600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">那種所謂的通訊方法</p>
<p begin="11165400000t" end="11192200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">應該是只能跟總部聯繫的通訊方法</p>
<p begin="11193000000t" end="11204600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">而且媽媽根本不知道</p>
<p begin="11205400000t" end="11226600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">被送走的兄弟姐妹的下落</p>
<p begin="11231800000t" end="11249000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">更別說是進去找線索</p>
<p begin="11255800000t" end="11263400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">出了問題</p>
<p begin="11264200000t" end="11282200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">發訊器還可能會暴露我們的行動</p>
<p begin="11290600000t" end="11313800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">我們也不清楚那房間的保安狀況</p>
<p begin="11314600000t" end="11334200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">這樣做太危險了　　但是…</p>
<p begin="11339000000t" end="11351800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">我剛才說了這麼多的意思</p>
<p begin="11352600000t" end="11371000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">即是風險明顯高於回報</p>
<p begin="11389400000t" end="11423400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">沒錯，現在還需要對修女保持警惕</p>
<p begin="11424200000t" end="11447800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">所以我們不要輕舉妄動，自掘墳墓</p>
<p begin="11448600000t" end="11457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">說得對</p>
<p begin="11461400000t" end="11481800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">雖然我現在還可以壓制著媽媽</p>
<p begin="11482600000t" end="11501800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">但是讓修女識破的話就完蛋了</p>
<p begin="11507400000t" end="11518200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">大家要記著這一點</p>
<p begin="11563000000t" end="11596600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">阿唐，你可以先去準備晚飯嗎</p>
<p begin="11597400000t" end="11606600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">沒有人過去的話</p>
<p begin="11607400000t" end="11618600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">媽媽會…　　我知道了</p>
<p begin="11788600000t" end="11800200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">阿唐，那邊…</p>
<p begin="11849000000t" end="11867800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">你真的打算進去？</p>
<p begin="11868600000t" end="11893400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">我沒辦法像他們那樣冷靜</p>
<p begin="11913000000t" end="11941400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">而且我很想知道媽媽的真面目</p>
<p begin="12183800000t" end="12204600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">就是這個書架的後面有暗門</p>
<p begin="12290600000t" end="12305400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">要怎樣才能打開</p>
<p begin="12389800000t" end="12404600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">真的有暗門嗎</p>
<p begin="12413000000t" end="12437400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">可惡，我們明明要儘早想辦法</p>
<p begin="12438200000t" end="12457800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">離開這裡去救他們</p>
<p begin="12463800000t" end="12476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">難道是要…</p>
<p begin="12507000000t" end="12530200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">我們要細心觀察它的形狀</p>
<p begin="12623400000t" end="12631800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">走吧</p>
<p begin="12681800000t" end="12692600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">門是鎖著的</p>
<p begin="12915800000t" end="12939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">(泛紅的天空)</p>
<p begin="12940600000t" end="12977800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">(如今看來如此恐怖)</p>
<p begin="12983000000t" end="13002600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">(若不知曉)</p>
<p begin="13003400000t" end="13038200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">(是否就能幸福度日)</p>
<p begin="13044200000t" end="13117000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">(又一盞溫暖的燈火悄悄熄滅)</p>
<p begin="13117800000t" end="13157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">(不知不覺中失去了)</p>
<p begin="13157800000t" end="13217000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">(曾經誤信過　那溫柔的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13217800000t" end="13251400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">(那曾是我的一切)</p>
<p begin="13252200000t" end="13317800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">(憑著揮灑的汗水與熾熱的心)</p>
<p begin="13318600000t" end="13385800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">(我們的確抱著意志生存)</p>
<p begin="13386600000t" end="13424600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">(事到如今　還說甚麼想要你的愛)</p>
<p begin="13425400000t" end="13453000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">(動起來　不聽使喚的雙腿)</p>
<p begin="13453800000t" end="13486200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">(脫離這個牢籠)</p>
<p begin="13487000000t" end="13519800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">(抓緊明天的自由)</p>
<p begin="13520600000t" end="13551800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">(走出絕望的困境)</p>
</div>
